{"tid":1005520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國採購戰機2選1 F-35出局","createTime":"2019-02-02T09:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T11:49:42.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7047b70ada08fbdb1de4aba8a955e84d8e374bb0","tid":1005520,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"青年日報<br />\n青年日報\t<br />\n688 人追蹤<br />\n青年日報社<br />\n2019年2月2日 上午12:00<br />\n留言<br />\n編譯郭正原／綜合外電報導<br />\n<br />\n據《金融時報》1日報導，雖然先前德空軍高層表態，認為洛馬生產的F-35戰機，是取代現役老舊的「龍捲風」戰機首選，但受政治因素考量已「確定出局」。消息來源指出，德空軍將在歐洲合作的「颱風」（EF-2000）與波音生產的「超級大黃蜂」（F/A-18E/F）2款戰機擇一。<br />\n<br />\n危及合作計畫 法反對德買F-35<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，德空軍從原本4款候選機型範圍縮小至EF-2000與F/A-18E/F，F-35與F-15皆已出局。尤其法國極力反對德國購買F-35，強調會危及法德新一代戰機合作計畫。要被取代的現役「龍捲風」戰機主要為「阻絕打擊型」（IDS）與「電戰偵察型」（ECR），總數約85架，隸屬於戰鬥轟炸機聯隊。<br />\n<br />\n由於對空巴集團與波音來說可謂大單，因此德國防部將在獲得廠商報價與相關性能訊息後，才會進行下一個階段的評估。同時，德國承擔北約共同防衛義務，又是「核武共享」政策的一員，因此其選擇的新機，必須具備投射美軍B61核子炸彈的能力。<br />\n<br />\nEF-2000目前尚未具投射B61炸彈能力，可謂一大劣勢，不過EF-2000為德空軍現役空優機種，後勤方面已「搶占先機」，加上德軍有意替換最舊的33架EF-2000，顯然更具利基。據稱僅替換這33架EF-2000，價值就高達34億美元（約新臺幣1054億元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/U_GXhtgZlXfUCwuGtLnnLw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTM0O2g9NTUw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/youthdailynews_517/8cfa424d5c947da6151ab0a0386ccfa0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FU_GXhtgZlXfUCwuGtLnnLw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTM0O2g9NTUw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fyouthdailynews_517%2F8cfa424d5c947da6151ab0a0386ccfa0&h=f0006c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以歐洲合作的EF-2000戰機取代「龍捲風」目前呼聲頗高，加上德空軍也打算替換較早服役的33架戰機，相對來說更具優勢。（達志影像／美聯社資料照片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OB4YG3v5um9ZfpLH89MQ7g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTM0O2g9NTUw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/youthdailynews_517/b193473f2c4d321e63af8fd2b89f9989\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOB4YG3v5um9ZfpLH89MQ7g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTM0O2g9NTUw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fyouthdailynews_517%2Fb193473f2c4d321e63af8fd2b89f9989&h=422a300c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波音產製的「超級大黃蜂」為美國海軍所採用，功能齊全的特性讓防空、對地打擊甚至電子作戰也難不倒它。（取自DVIDS網站）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gyap3bpcPEZWuKRij40Efg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTM0O2g9NTUw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/youthdailynews_517/204f07412e7478f014d237f5d73e773e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fgyap3bpcPEZWuKRij40Efg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTM0O2g9NTUw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fyouthdailynews_517%2F204f07412e7478f014d237f5d73e773e&h=0bb55445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德空軍「龍捲風」機隊約在1983年起開始服役，目前主要隸屬於戰鬥轟炸聯隊。（達志影像／美聯社資料照片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F2%E9%81%B81-f-35%E5%87%BA%E5%B1%80-160000271.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F2%25E9%2581%25B81-f-35%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B1%2580-160000271.html&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2aCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=350c8464\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F2%E9%81%B81-f-35%E5%87%BA%E5%B1%80-160000271.html</a>"},{"pid":"bbc6de802562594a11ec8c703a02648c4d5e3412","tid":1005520,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:00:19.000Z","msg":"F18玩左40年仲有得玩 F35玩左十零年就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da283d5031270c575e48ab6efddcf44541811ffb","tid":1005520,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:11:23.000Z","msg":"德軍要靠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希特拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e71e7c53314916eae076c1db708350b040b118e","tid":1005520,"uid":50873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:34:07.000Z","msg":"颱風個項目德國自己都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n選佢都好合理"},{"pid":"406b5d0c4e8d04802b0fc8ef7a3cdbd802b1db51","tid":1005520,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbc6de802562594a11ec8c703a02648c4d5e3412","tid":1005520,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:00:19.000Z","msg":"F18玩左40年仲有得玩 F35玩左十零年就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}